Lisa Ann https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lisa_Ann 0 Lisa Ann (born May 9, 1972) is an American pornographic actress and radio personality. She has also worked as a director and talent agent. She has received mainstream notice for parodying former Alaska governor Sarah Palin in six adult films. She is a member of the AVN, XRCO, and Urban X Halls of Fame.
